Nord Pool, Regulators Form Joint Council for Power Regulation

-- B y   L a r s   P a u l s s o n
-- 
2011-05-24T14:24:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-24/nord-pool-regulators-form-joint-council-for-power-regulation.html
Nord Pool Spot AS , which runs
electricity markets in the Nordic area, formed a joint council
with energy regulators in the region to exchange market
information and discuss regulatory issues.  Norway ,  Sweden ,  Denmark ,  Finland  and  Estonia  are
represented on the council and Antti Paananen, director general
of the Finnish Energy Market Authority, was elected chairman,
the Oslo-based exchange said today on its  website .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lars Paulsson in London at 
 lpaulsson@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stephen Voss on 
 sev@bloomberg.net  